      "text": "Melanie had a setback last month and had to take a break from pottery, which is her way of self-expression and finding peace.",
      "category": "event",
      "importance": "high"
    },
    {
      "fact_id": "F4",
      "text": "Melanie has been using reading and painting as creative outlets to stay busy during her break from pottery.",
      "category": "state_change",
      "importance": "medium"
    },
    {
      "fact_id": "F5",
      "text": "Caroline recently attended a transgender poetry reading that was powerful and empowering.",
      "category": "event",
      "importance": "high"
    },
    {
      "fact_id": "F6",
      "text": "The poetry reading was a safe place for self-expression and celebrated transgender identities.",
      "category": "event",
      "importance": "medium"
    },
    {
